         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Hatres to Heras his brother, greeting. In accordance with your instructions concerning Serenus the fuller who is working with Phileas, if you have need of him send a servant for him today, the 19th. Do not neglect this, as I am keeping him. I pray for your health and prosperity. (Addressed) Deliver to Heras. (Grenfell &amp; Hunt)</ab>
